{
NPCText "There probably isn't anything that *can* be done about it - *cough* - even though you fixed his Autodoc for us."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why are there so many sick people living here?" linkto "Jon_2_2b_1"  notes ""
