Node "Jon_2_2b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Sandover has become a kind of haven for the desperate and outcast, *cough, cough*. No-one bothers us much because the rads are higher here than they are in most of the rest of the wastes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You sound ill yourself." linkto "Jon_2_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How dangerous is the radiation in Sandover?" linkto "Jon_2_2b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What else can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Jon_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be going. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_2_2b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Relax, stranger. It takes months and years of living here before the rads start taking their toll. *Cough.* You're in no real danger if you're just passing through."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You sound ill yourself, though." linkto "Jon_2_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What else can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Jon_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be going. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_2_2c_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Not much. *Cough.* If you're looking for work, you should speak to Saman."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why?" linkto "Jon_2_2c_2a"  notes "If the PC has already completed the 'Fix the Autodoc' quest, go to Jon_2_2c_2b instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What else can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Jon_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You sound ill yourself." linkto "Jon_2_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why are there so many sick people in Sandover?" linkto "Jon_2_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be going. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_2_2c_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Dr. Oswald is having a problem with his Autodoc. *Cough, cough.* I'm sure he'd be grateful for your help, if you know your way around gadgetry."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find Saman?" linkto "Jon_2_2a_3b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who is Dr. Oswald?" linkto "Jon_2_2a_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What else can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Jon_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You sound ill yourself." linkto "Jon_2_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why are there so many sick people in Sandover?" linkto "Jon_2_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be going. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_2_2c_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I should imagine that he could find some other work for you, now that - *cough, cough* - you've fixed Dr. Oswald's Autodoc for us."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where can I find Saman?" linkto "Jon_2_2a_3b_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What else can you tell me about Sandover?" linkto "Jon_3_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You sound ill yourself." linkto "Jon_2_2a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why are there so many sick people in Sandover?" linkto "Jon_2_2b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be going. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_1"
notes "The Jon_3_* path is where the PC can find out about Jonathan's interest in the history of the area, which leads to the 'Find out about Sandover's history' quest."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I've always been interested in Sandover's history, ever since I moved here. There are a lot of ruined buildings in the surrounding area; it must have been quite a place before the war."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What have you learned about Sandover so far?" linkto "Jon_3_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Most of what I've heard about Sandover is how the place was founded, which was a long time after the war."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What can you tell me about that?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any idea what was here before the war?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There are a lot of ruined buildings in the surrounding area; it must have been quite a place before the war."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Have you had much opportunity to explore them?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Not half as much as I'd have liked. *Cough, cough.* I'm too old to wander far from the caves now. It's a damn shame - the answers to so many questions about the past lie in the few square miles around here, I'm sure."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you think there is to find around here that would tell you about the past?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Pretty much any artefacts, *cough*, from before the war. The big finds are usually paper documents, though. Anything that details what day-to-day life was like."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How hard are they to find?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Very hard. *Cough.* Especially documents. Most of those that weren't destroyed by the bombs just crumbled to dust in the following years. No, anything made of paper would need to be buried away somewhere cool, dark and dry to survive since the war."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll be doing some looking around whilst I'm in the area. If I find anything that could help you, I'll bring it back." linkto "Jon_3_3a_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_5"
notes "The PC gets the 'Find out about Sandover's history' quest."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Would you? That would be marvelous! *Cough, cough.* I don't have much to offer in return, but I'd do what I could to reimburse you."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You needn't worry about paying me. I'd gladly do it for free." linkto "Jon_3_3a_6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Talking of the local area, do you know where I could find the General Atomics International base?" linkto "Jon_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3a_6"
notes "The PC gets the 'Find out about Sandover's history' quest."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Stranger, you're too kind. You've made this old man... *cough.* Well, you've made me cough, but 'very happy' is what I meant to say. *Cough, cough.*"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Talking of the local area, do you know where I could find the General Atomics International base?" linkto "Jon_4_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Take it easy, Jonathan. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Unfortunately, *cough,* because all of Sandover's history is passed on by word of mouth and nothing is written down, it's hard to know exactly what is true."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me what you know." linkto "Jon_3_3b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any idea what was here before the war?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Apparently, a small group of people became unpopular in its home town and was exiled into the wastes. They travelled aimlessly for several weeks, before they stumbled upon this cave network. [He coughs and points to the cave entrance behind you both.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why were they exiled?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did they survive for so long in the wastes?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any idea what was here before the war?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_3_3b_3a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Desparate for water, they found access to an underground stream at the bottom of the caves. They recovered slowly and realized they had no place else to go. They set up camp here, above ground."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3a_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why were they exiled from their home town?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did they survive for so long in the wastes?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any idea what was here before the war?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
