Node "Jon_3_3b_3a_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It wasn't long before they established contact with some of the local towns. The settlers sold what scavenge they found in order to survive, and the other towns generally left Sandover alone otherwise, for fear of the radiation here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[MORE]" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3a_5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why were they exiled from their home town?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3b"  notes ""
