Node "Jon_3_3b_3a_5"
notes "Increment the node Jon_Historian by 1. This means the PC can now tell the museum curator in Rusty Springs (exact nature of NPC not known at time of writing) that Jonathan is knowledgable of Sandover's history."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Within a few years of the first settlers arriving here, word of the Sandover encampment spread out along the trade routes. Other people began to turn up, telling their own tales of exile and rejection. Sandover expanded from a mere campsite and became a town in its own right."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why were the original settlers exiled from their home town?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did they survive for so long in the wastes?" linkto "Jon_3_3b_3c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Do you have any idea what was here before the war?" linkto "Jon_3_3a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Jon_9"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
