Node "Jon_6_2b_2a_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That's appalling! *Cough, cough.* What else can you tell me about this horrible religion?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The cult sprang up in the last few months before the war. It tried to appease its gods with blood sacrifice to try to prevent the war from happening." linkto "Jon_6_2b_2a_2"  notes "More feasible. Milder Barter check. If failed, go to Jon_6_2b_9_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It was nearly two thousand years old. It looks like human sacrifice and even cannibalism were commonplace." linkto "Jon_6_2b_2a_2"  notes "Less feasible. Harder Barter check. If failed, go to Jon_6_2b_9_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't want to give the item to you, though." linkto "Jon_6_2c"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Jon_6_2b_2a_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "*Cough! Cough!* I had no idea pre-war man was so barbaric. Wait, *cough,* how did you find this information out?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "There was an old computer near to where I found the relic. It had a complete history of the cult." linkto "Jon_6_2b_2a_3"  notes "Does the PC look like a computery type to Jonathan? Moderate science skill check. If failed, go to Jon_6_2b_9_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found the relic in an abandoned, pre-war, underground temple. You could still see the blood on the walls, but there were also carvings which told of the religion's history." linkto "Jon_6_2b_2a_3"  notes "Does the PC look like a linguistics expert to Jonathan? Moderate Speech skill check. If failed, go to Jon_6_2b_9_1 instead."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't want to give the item to you, though." linkto "Jon_6_2c"  notes ""
              }
}
