          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "He's given me a holodisk, which I can use with my Pipboy to take a recording of your voice. He would like to hear what you know about Sandover's history." linkto "Jon_7_2b_1" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE Jon_Free_Papers == 0 link_next NONE } notes ""
